    helpText: 'Converting quarter life uncertainty into a structured timeline transforms overwhelming possibilities into manageable monthly goals with clear progress markers. Break down your major transition into 6 specific monthly milestones, including concrete actions like skill development, networking targets, financial goals, or lifestyle changes. This detailed roadmap provides accountability and motivation while allowing you to track real progress during this transformative period, helping you move from feeling stuck to actively building the life you want.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-44',
    prompt: 'Complete a "values conflict audit" by identifying where your daily actions don\'t align with your stated priorities',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Quarter life crises often stem from unconsciously living according to others\' expectations rather than your own values, creating internal tension and dissatisfaction. Spend one week tracking how you actually spend your time, then compare this reality against your stated values and priorities to identify specific disconnects. This audit reveals where you might be saying yes to things that don\'t serve you and where you need to reallocate your energy to create a life that feels authentic and fulfilling.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-45',
    prompt: 'Sign up for and complete one professional development challenge or program that pushes you outside your comfort zone',
